{"tid":1997851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Bill Gates替中国說話  班農 : 與魔鬼北京站在一起","createTime":"2020-05-02T03:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T15:20:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc315283dfe9d6da7410b97e60b80c8bf222377","tid":1997851,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:23:58.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情全球延燒，世界各國開始研議要調查病毒源頭，先後多國都有意向中國究責索賠，但微軟公司創辦人比爾．蓋茲（Bill Gates）近日受訪時替中國說話，對於全球究責中國的問題，他認為「現在不是指責中國的時候」，此話也讓前白宮首席策士班農（Steve Bannon）氣得砲轟，「與魔鬼北京站在一起」。<br />\n<br />\n比爾蓋茲4月26日接受《CNN》訪問時表示，美國近日將砲火對準中國，不斷指出中國沒有清楚表示病毒來源，這是共和黨故意要轉移焦點。比爾蓋茲認為，「中國如其他國家一樣，在病毒一開始出現時做對了很多事，也不可否認日後他們回頭看時可以清楚點出幾點疏忽的地方。」<br />\n<br />\n對於主持人詢問，「有人指責中國在疫情期間掩蓋真相，應該對此負責，你有什麼看法？」比爾蓋茲回應說，現在怪罪中國，目前一昧批評中國是「不正確和不公平」，這樣做只是想「分散注意力」，他也批評美國這次防疫表現「特別糟糕」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，前白宮首席策士班農在自媒體上痛批，比爾蓋茲跟北京魔鬼站在一起，他說，去年12月，中國李文亮醫生就在微信發出警告說，「武漢出現不明肺炎病例」，台灣收到李文亮的訊息後也在去年底向WHO寄發電子郵件，警告武漢病毒患者需要被隔離，這句話充分暗示病毒可以人傳人。<br />\n<br />\n班農更不客氣地批評，對於這些預先警告，中國視而不見，蓋茲也視而不見，「蓋茲就是個騙子」。<br />\n<br />\n    Bill Gates claims that criticisms of how China lied and covered up the coronavirus is a &ldquo;distraction&rdquo;: &ldquo;China did a lot of things right at the beginning &hellip; they avoided the incredible economic pain &hellip; I think there&rsquo;s a lot of incorrect and unfair things said&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n    This is all a lie <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/RlbwV0fUcA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FRlbwV0fUcA&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw120Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=c08168a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/RlbwV0fUcA</a><br />\n    &mdash; Ryan Saavedra （@RealSaavedra） April 26, 2020<br />\n<br />\n    Steve Bannon RIPS Bill Gates: &ldquo;We&rsquo;re coming after you as a stone cold liar!&rdquo; @CitizensAR #WarRoomPandemic <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/ddxzFGhYW9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FddxzFGhYW9&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw120Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=3e3e355f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/ddxzFGhYW9</a><br />\n    &mdash; themissionisgreat （@missionisgreat） April 27, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3152473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3152473&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw120Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=2232875d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3152473&h=1a5f6454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3152473</a>"},{"pid":"0ad921e29a5abfa7c88de8bdc17df39a0295d908","tid":1997851,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:26:15.000Z","msg":"抗疫後：既然抗疫成功 點解仲要追究中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0f8d02dee9780e9e04f0f6573a9959328a9384","tid":1997851,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"但 bill gates 影響力大班農1萬倍<br />\n<br />\n擔心..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d306df78b7dadd7e98f360184225c613841162","tid":1997851,"uid":292644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">俾人做緊</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=prvmtwBCy_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DprvmtwBCy_w&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw120Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=fb464e75\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=prvmtwBCy_w</a>"},{"pid":"3baa6689ba4adbb033b29e748a389803b79cdd02","tid":1997851,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" cla